FIRST PROGRAM (CALCULATOR PERFORMING AIRTHMETIC OPERATION )
The program having libereries .
it has define a simple calculator in "main method.
Using main method "Scanner " object named  read to user input .
Three  variables use num1,num2,num3,doublenum are stored .
We using loop conditions for performing multiples calculations .
We using swith statement for the taken input of Airhmetic operation one by one .
User give input expression of Airthmetic operation or "exit" to quit .
The input expression is "split"into token (sepreated by spaces ).
The program parse first number ,operator and second number from the token .
If user input a "exit" the program displays farwell message and terminates.
